These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, australian, american, british, indonesian, polish, spanish
1. the australian is in the middle##1
2. the australian is on the left of the american##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the british##1
4. the turkish is on the right of the american##1
5. the spanish is on the far left##1
6. the polish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | spanish | british | indonesian | australian | american | turkish | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  freelancer, scientist, project-manager, bartender, musician, fisherman, firefighter
1. the firefighter is on the far right##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the musician##1
4. the musician is on the left of the project-manager##1
5. the bartender is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the firefighter is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | freelancer | musician | project-manager | fisherman | bartender | scientist | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, photography, writing, puzzles, collecting, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | traveling | collecting | photography | magic-tricks | dancing | writing |

 #################################

 
