1. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | hamster | frog | pony | fish | bird | rabbit | horse |

