.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, animation, western, action, spy, zombie
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | action | martial-arts | epic | spy | western | zombie | animation |

